View of apartment buildings in the resort town of Kusadasi on the Aegean Sea. The population of the town increases from 65,000 to 500,000 during the tourist season. Kusadasi is about a 20-minute drive from the Roman ruins at Ephesus.



DimensionsFile SizeDownload


